o%20flags%20a%20remark%20by%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%20aka%20The%20Rebel%20Kid%20in%20which%20she%20spoke%20of%20the%20food%20habits%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20eat%20dog%20meat%20even%20though%20I%20have%20never%20tasted%20it.%20I%20know%20because%20my%20friends%20eat%20it.%20They%20even%20eat%20their%20pets%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20quotes%20her%20as%20saying%20and%20adds%20that%20such%20remarks%20endanger%20peace%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamay%20Raina%2C%20the%20complaint%20says%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20jury%20and%20the%20production%20of%20the%20show%20and%20also%20shared%20videos%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20complaint%20also%20names%20YouTuber%20Ashish%20Chanchlani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanmati%20Pandey%20clarified%20that%20his%20phone%20number%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20that%20streamed%20the%20roast%20show%2C%20but%20he%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20content%20creation.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%2C%20which%20erupted%20after%20a%20video%20from%20the%20show%20went%20viral%2C%20is%20showing%20no%20sign%20of%20dying%20down.%20Assam%20Police%2C%20too%2C%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20this%20connection%20and%20a%20team%20from%20the%20state%20has%20come%20to%20Mumbai%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApoorva%20Mukhija%20today%20visited%20Khar%20police%20station%20with%20her%20lawyer%20and%20recorded%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%20and%20summoned%20him%20and%20others%20linked%20to%20the%20show%20on%20February%2017.%20%26quot%3BThese%20comments%2C%20which%20have%20sparked%20widespread%20public%20outrage%2C%20violate%20the%20dignity%20and%20respect%20owed%20to%20every%20individual%2C%20particularly%20in%20a%20society%20that%20upholds%20equality%20and%20mutual%20respect%2