f%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAravind%20Srinivas%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20share%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20meeting%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BGreat%20meeting%20you%20%40sundarpichai.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGreat%20meeting%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsundarpichai%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40sundarpichai%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZ0yzYhsHgd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZ0yzYhsHgd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aravind%20Srinivas%20(%40AravSrinivas)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAravSrinivas%2Fstatus%2F1889309624861331525%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2011%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20were%20abuzz%20with%20excitement%20as%20the%20photo%20went%20viral.%20Many%20took%20to%20the%20comments%20section%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts%20on%20the%20meeting%2C%20with%20some%20users%20suggesting%20that%20the%20two%20tech%20leaders%20should%20collaborate%20to%20create%20the%20ultimate%20search%20engine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20has%20funds%2C%20and%20you%20have%20the%20best%20team%20to%20work%20on%20and%20better%20AI%20for%20humanity%20not%20just%20for%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20you%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20switched%20from%20Google%20Assistant%20to%20Perplexity%20Assistant%20on%20his%20Apple%20phone%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0A%20third%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLooks%20like%20an%20incredible%20moment!%20Must've%20been%20a%20great%20conversation.%26quot%3B%20A%20fourth%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BChennai%20Express%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20a%20fifth%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20you%20speak%20in%20Tamil%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20Mr%20Pichai%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparis-ai-summit-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-meets-pm-modi-in-paris-7689823%5C%22%3Emet%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20highlighted%20the%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20opportunities%26quot%3B%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20will%20bring%20to%20India.%C2%A0The%20Alphabet%20CEO%20also%20noted%20the%20potential%20for%20close%20collaboration%20between%20Google%20and%20India%20to%20advance%20the%20country's%20digital%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20Delighted%20to%20meet%20with%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20while%20in%20Paris%20for%20the%20AI%20Action%20Summit.%20We%20discussed%20the%20incredible%20opportunities%20AI%20will%20bring%20to%20India%20and%20ways%20we%20can%20work%20closely%20together%20on%20India's%20digital%20transformation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Mr%20Pichai%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Google%20and%20Alphabet%2C%20leading%20the%20company's%20innovation%20and%20growth%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%20Born%20in%20Madurai%2C%20Mr%20Pichai%20has%20risen%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20tech%20leaders%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Aravind%20Srinivas%20is%20the%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Perplexity%20AI%2C%20a%20cutting-edge%20AI-powered%20search%20engine%20backed%20by%20prominent%20investors%2C%20including%20Jeff%20Bezos.%20Founded%20in%202022%2C%20Perplexity%20AI%20was%20established%20by%20Srinivas%20alongside%20Andy%20Konwinski%2C%20Denis%20Yarats%2C%20and%20Johnny%20Ho.%20A%20distinguished%20alumnus%20of%20IIT-Madras%2C%20Srinivas%20earned%20his%20PhD%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%20His%20career%20began%20as%20a%20research%20intern%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20followed%20by%20stints%20at%20Google%20and%20DeepMind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2