g%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20first-year%20students%20were%20forced%20to%20stand%20naked%20while%20their%20seniors%20hung%20dumbbells%20from%20their%20private%20parts.%20The%20victims%20were%20also%20subjected%20to%20injuries%20using%20sharp%20objects%2C%20including%20a%20compass%20from%20a%20geometry%20box.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cruelty%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20Lotion%20was%20applied%20to%20the%20wounds%2C%20causing%20pain.%20When%20the%20victims%20screamed%20in%20agony%2C%20the%20lotion%20was%20forcibly%20smeared%20into%20their%20mouths.%20The%20seniors%20allegedly%20filmed%20these%20acts%20and%20threatened%20the%20juniors%20with%20dire%20consequences%2C%20including%20jeopardising%20their%20academic%20futures%2C%20if%20they%20dared%20to%20report%20the%20abuse.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20claims%20that%20the%20seniors%20regularly%20extorted%20money%20from%20the%20juniors%20on%20Sundays%20to%20buy%20alcohol.%20Those%20who%20refused%20to%20comply%20were%20beaten.%20One%20student%2C%20unable%20to%20bear%20the%20harassment%20any%20longer%2C%20informed%20his%20father%2C%20who%20then%20encouraged%20him%20to%20approach%20the%20police.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20are%20currently%20in%20police%20custody%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20produced%20before%20a%20magistrate%20by%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20weeks%20after%20a%2015-year-old%20schoolboy%20in%20Kochi%20died%20by%20suicide.%20The%20student's%20mother%20alleged%20that%20her%20son%20was%20bullied%20by%20students%20which%20pushed%20him%20towards%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739345280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ftrfr9ni_kerala-ragging-row-_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-ragging-dumbbells-hung-from-private-parts-ragging-horror-at-kerala-medical-college-7691484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2