e%20Charcha%20that%20it%20is%20natural%20to%20feel%20stress%2C%20but%20important%20to%20know%20how%20to%20handle%20it.%20While%20admitting%20that%20she%20was%20weak%20at%20math%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20lucky%20to%20have%20parents%20who%20did%20not%20focus%20much%20on%20her%20getting%20good%20marks.%20She%20also%20stressed%20the%20need%20importance%20of%20friends%20and%20a%20community%20in%20helping%20deal%20with%20anxiety.%20%26quot%3BParents%20have%20to%20understand%20that%20a%20child's%20interest%20may%20lie%20in%20something%20else%2C%20and%20that%20is%20ok%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20an%20interactive%20session%2C%20the%20Ms%20Padukone%20conducted%20an%20activity%20where%20students%20wrote%20their%20strengths%20on%20pieces%20of%20paper%20and%20displayed%20them%20on%20a%20board.%20%26quot%3BThis%20activity%20helps%20you%20realise%20that%20if%20you%20focus%20on%20your%20strengths%20rather%20than%20weaknesses%2C%20you'll%20see%20how%20many%20things%20you're%20good%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20competition%20is%20a%20part%20of%20life%2C%20but%20the%20ultimate%20endeavour%20should%20be%20to%20recognise%20our%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20and%20challenge%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20her%20mental%20health%20journey%2C%20the%20Piku%20actor%20said%20that%20she%20started%20feeling%20free%20and%20light%20when%20she%20began%20talking%20about%20her%20feelings.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20dealing%20with%20exams%20too%2C%20expressing%20helps.%20Focus%20on%20things%20that%20are%20in%20your%20control.%20And%20talked%20to%20your%20parents%20or%20someone%20you%20trust%20if%20you%20feel%20stressed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stressing%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20not%20being%20afraid%20of%20failure%20and%20enjoying%20what%20you%20like%20to%20do%2C%20Ms%20Padukone%20also%20shared%20a%20hack%20with%20students%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20present.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20is%20called%205%2C%204%2C%203%2C%202%2C%201.%20Five%20things%20you%20can%20see%20around%20you%2C%20four%20things%20you%20can%20touch%2C%20three%20things%20you%20can%20hear%2C%20two%20things%20you%20can%20smell%2C%20one%20thing%20you%20can%20taste%20.%20They%20bring%20you%20back%20in%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversation%20with%20students%2C%20she%20shared%20her%20strong%20inclination%20towards%20sports%20and%20extracurricular%20activities.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20very%20naughty%20child.%20Even%20today%2C%20my%20parents%20say%20that%20you%20will%20never%20find%20Deepika%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%20I%20was%20always%20jumping%20from%20sofas%2C%20tables%2C%20and%20chairs.%20I%20was%20more%20interested%20in%20extracurricular%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20the%20eighth%20edition%20of%20'Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha'%20on%20February%2010%20in%20Delhi%2C%20interacting%20with%20students%20at%20Sunder%20Nursery%20during%20the%20first%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20significance%20of%20technology%2C%20he%20had%20encouraged%20students%20to%20understand%20and%20make%20optimal%20use%20of%20it.%20%26quot%3BA%20student's%20life%20does%20not%20stop%20if%20they%20fail%20an%20exam.%20One%20must%20decide%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20succeed%20in%20life%20or%20books.%20You%20should%20turn%20your%20failures%20into%20your%20teachers.%20You%20are%20fortunate%20to%20be%20born%20in%20an%20era%20of%20technology%2C%20and%20our%20focus%20should%20be%20to%20understanding%20technology%20and%20have%20an%20optimum%20utilisation%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739342700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fap59tagg_deepika-padukone_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeepika-padukone-to-students-on-pariksha-pe-charcha-sleep-express-hydrate-medit