less%20messaging%20from%20Bombardier%20Ryan%20Mason%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20intense%20period%20of%20unwelcome%20behaviour%26quot%3B%20and%20concluded%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Balmost%20certain%26quot%3B%20that%20this%20harassment%20contributed%20to%20her%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20message%20to%20Gunner%20Beck%2C%20on%20October%2021%2C%20Mason%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BLove%20you%20Jayse.%20As%20a%20friend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20on%20November%2011%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20amazing%20Jayse%2C%20I%20appreciate%20you%20so%20much%2C%20I%20love%20everything%20about%20you%2C%20even%20your%20flaws.%20I%20will%20always%20be%20there%20along%20for%20the%20ride%20with%20you%2C%20I%20have%20said%20it%20before%20but%20you're%20stuck%20with%20me%20forever%20now.%20I%20love%20you%20as%20a%20friend%2C%20I%20love%20you.%26quot%3B%20On%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2025%2C%20Gunner%20Beck%20wrote%20to%20Mr%20Mason%2C%20telling%20him%20the%20situation%20was%20%26quot%3Bbecoming%20a%20bit%20too%20much%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bweighing%20me%20down%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeighann%20McCready%20revealed%20that%20her%20daughter%20had%20become%20increasingly%20unsettled%20by%20these%20messages.%20According%20to%20McCready%2C%20Mr%20Mason%20was%20taking%20advantage%20of%20Ms%20Beck's%20friendly%20nature%2C%20crossing%20boundaries%20and%20making%20her%20feel%20uncomfortable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20report%20suggested%20that%20the%20earlier%20incident%20at%20Thorney%20Island%2C%20where%20Ms%20Beck%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20by%20BSM%20Michael%20Webber%2C%20may%20have%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20her%20willingness%20to%20report%20subsequent%20incidents.%20Lance%20Bombardier%20Kirsty%20Davis%20recounted%20that%20she%C2%A0received%2020%20missed%20calls%20from%20Ms%20Beck%20before%20they%20finally%20spoke%2C%20and%20during%20their%20conversation%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20a%20traumatic%20incident%20had%20occurred%20earlier%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Davis%2C%20Ms%20Beck%20said%20that%20after%20a%20gathering%20had%20dwindled%2C%20she%20was%20left%20alone%20with%20BSM%20Michael%20Webber%2C%20who%20attempted%20to%20kiss%20her%20despite%20her%20protests.%20Webber%20allegedly%20pinned%20Ms%20Beck%20down%2C%20ignoring%20her%20attempts%20to%20push%20him%20away.%20Ms%20Beck%20told%20Ms%20Davis%20that%20Webber%20had%20tried%20to%20force%20himself%20on%20her%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conversation%20left%20her%20in%20tears%2C%20visibly%20upset%20and%20frightened.%20Ms%20Davis%20also%20recalled%20that%20Beck%20was%20reluctant%20to%20end%20the%20phone%20call%2C%20which%20lasted%20throughout%20the%20night%20and%20expressed%20concern%20that%20Webber%20might%20come%20to%20her%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20testimony%2C%20Leighann%20McCready%20revealed%20that%20her%20daughter%20had%20called%20her%20just%20eight%20days%20before%20her%20death%20while%20staying%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Newbury%20for%20work.%20During%20the%20call%2C%20Ms%20Beck%20expressed%20her%20growing%20paranoia%2C%20believing%20that%20Bombardier%20Ryan%20Mason%20had%20tracked%20her%20phone%20and%20was%20eavesdropping%20on%20her%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCready%20shared%20that%20Ms%20Beck%20felt%20utterly%20%26quot%3Bfreaked%20out%26quot%3B%20by%20Mason's%20behaviour%2C%20which%20had%20escalated%20to%20the%20point%20where%20she%20felt%20trapped%20and%20helpless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20drafted%20text%20to%20Mason%2C%20that%20she%20did%20not%20end%20up%20sending%2C%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20tried%20to%20act%20as%20normal%20as%20possible%20because%20we%20are%20working%20together%2C%20but%20nothing%20%5Bis%5D%20normal%20about%20this%20situation.%20It's%20possessive%20and%20psychotic%2C%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20it's%20not%20normal%20behaviour.%20I%20am%20struggling%20to%20deal%20with%20all%20of%20this.%20It's%20taking%20a%20huge%20toll%20on%20my%20mental%20health%20for%20many%20personal%20reasons.%20I%20need%20time%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739340420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F3vlg82e8_jaysley-beck_625x300_12_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fteen-soldier-who-died-received-3-600-texts-from-possessive-boss-reveals-probe-report-7691311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Royal%20Artillery%20Gunner%20Jaysley%20Beck%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20Larkhill%20Camp%20in%20Wiltshire%20on%20December%2015%2C%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fteen-soldier-who-died-received-3-600-texts-from-possessive-boss-reveals-probe-report-7691311%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Korean%20designer%20Kim%20Rieul%20passes%20away%20at%2032%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739340184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118165666%2Cimgsize-26928.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fkorean-designer-kim-rieul-who-defined-k-pop-fashion-for-bts-and-more-passes-away-at-32%2Farticleshow%2F118165569.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118165569.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKim%20Rieul%2C%20a%20renowned%20hanbok%20designer%20for%20prominent%20K-pop%20idols%20like%20BTS%20and%20MONSTA%20X%2C%20passed%20away%20at%2032.%20Despite%20his%20initial%20disconnect%20from%20fashion%2C%20Kim%20gained%20recognition%20for%20his%20contemporary%20hanbok%20designs%2C%20significantly%20impacting%20the%20K-pop%20industry.%20His%20dedication%20and%20innovative%20approach%20leave%20a%20lasting%20legacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22