na%2Famp_articleshow%2F118161364.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLabourers%20In%20India%20Not%20Willing%20To%20Work%26quot%3B%3A%20L%26amp%3BT%20Chairman%20Sparks%20Row%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELarsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Chairman%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20another%20row%2C%20this%20time%20concerning%20the%20reluctance%20of%20workers%20to%20relocate%20owing%20to%20availability%20of%20government%20welfare%20schemes.%20This%20comes%20week%20after%20his%2090-hour%20work%20week%20remark%20led%20to%20a%20widespread%20debate%20about%20work-life%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20the%20CII's%20Mystic%20South%20Global%20Linkages%20Summit%202025%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20get%20workers%20for%20the%20construction%20industry%20as%20they%20are%20reluctant%20to%20travel%20from%20their%20hometown%20due%20to%20a%20preference%20for%20comfort.%20He%20said%20that%20schemes%20like%20MGNREGA%2C%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%20and%20JAN%20DHAN%20accounts%20likely%20affect%20labour%20mobilisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLabour%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20move%20for%20opportunities.%20Maybe%20their%20local%20economy%20is%20doing%20well%2C%20maybe%20it%20is%20due%20to%20the%20various%20government%20schemes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20shortage%20of%20labour%20would%20impact%20the%20building%20of%20India's%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subrahmanyan%20also%20said%20India%20faces%20the%20peculiar%20problem%20of%20migration%2C%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20requiring%204%20lakh%20workers%2C%20but%20recruiting%2016%20lakh%20people%20owing%20to%20attrition.%20He%20also%20raised%20the%20need%20to%20revise%20wages%20for%20workers%20in%20sync%20with%20inflation%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20Middle%20East%20draws%20workers%20as%20it%20draws%20three%20to%203.5%20times%20the%20salary%20they%20draw%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Chairman%20had%20said%20last%20month%20that%20he%20wants%20his%20employees%20to%20work%20on%20Sundays%20too.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20sitting%20at%20home%3F%20How%20long%20can%20you%20stare%20at%20your%20wife%3F%20Come%20on%2C%20get%20to%20the%20office%20and%20start%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20works%20on%20Sundays%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20saw%20many%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Adar%20Poonawalla%2C%20Anand%20Mahindra%20and%20ITC's%20Sanjiv%20Puri%2C%20advocating%20the%20need%20for%20work-life%20balance%20for%20productivity.%20The%20matter%20reached%20the%20Parliament%20when%20the%20government%20told%20Parliament%20last%20week%20that%20it%20is%20not%20considering%20any%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20maximum%20working%20hours%20to%2070%20or%2090%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20discourse%20over%2070-90-hour%20work%20week%2C%20pre-Budget%20Economic%20Survey%20on%20Friday%20last%20had%20cited%20studies%20to%20state%20that%20spending%20over%2060%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20work%20could%20have%20adverse%20health%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20noted%20that%20spending%20long%20hours%20at%20one's%20desk%20is%20detrimental%20to%20mental%20well-being%2C%20and%20individuals%20who%20spend%2012%20or%20more%20hours%20(per%20day)%20at%20a%20desk%20have%20distressed%20or%20struggling%20levels%20of%20mental%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739337000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fi8mncg4o_sn-subrahmanyan_625x300_10_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-90-hour-work-week-l-t-chief-kicks-up-workers-reluctance-row-7691123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SN%20Subrahmanyan%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20get%20workers%20for%20the%20construction%20industry%20as%20they%20are%20reluctant%20to%20travel%20from%20their%20hometown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-90-hour-work-week-l-t-chief-kicks-up-workers-reluctance-row-7691123%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDisrespecting%20Identity%20Not%20Fun%26quot%3B%3A%20Elvish%20Yadav's%20Remarks%20On%20Actor%20Spark%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20podcaster%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%2C%20another%20YouTuber%2C%20Elvish%20Yadav%2C%20is%20in%20trouble%20for%20his%20objectionable%20remarks%20against%20actor%20Chum%20Darang.%20The%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20women's%20commission%20chairperson%20has%20written%20to%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20seeking%20action%20against%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20in%20a%20podcast%2C%20Yadav%20had%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20against%20Chum%20Darang%20and%20also%20said%20she%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%26quot%3B%20name.%20Hitting%20back%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20actor%20said%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BDisrespecting%20someone's%20identity%20and%20name%20is%20not%20'fun'.%20Mocking%20someone's%20achievements%20is%20not%20'banter'.%20It's%20time%20we%20draw%20the%20line%20between%20humour%20and%20hate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20even%20more%20disappointing%20is%20that%20this%20wasn't%20just%20about%20my%20ethnicity.%20My%20hard%20work%20and%20a%20film%20backed%20by%20a%20visionary%20like%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali%20were%20also%20disrespected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChum%20Darang%20has%20worked%20in%20Bollywood%20movies%20Gangubai%20Kathiawadi%20and%20Badhaai%20Do.%20Mocking%20her%2C%20Yadav%20referred%20to%20her%20relationship%20with%20actor%20Karan%20Veer%20Mehra.%20%26quot%3BKaran%20Veer%C2%A0definitely%20had%20COVID%20because%20who%20even%20likes%20Chum%2C%20bro%3F%20Whose%20taste%20is%20that%20bad%3F%20Chum's%20name%20sounds%20so%20vulgar%E2%80%A6%20and%20she%20has%20worked%20in%20Gangubai%20Kathiawad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20After%20the%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20row%2C%20Yadav%20put%20out%20a%20clarification%20video%20that%20made%20it%20worse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20said%C2%A0he%20did%20not%20want%20any%20negativity%20and%20had%20got%20some%20parts%20removed%20from%20the%20podcast.%20He%20said%20it's%20surprising%20why%20%26quot%3Bsome%20people%20just%20don't%20get%20it%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20saying%20that%20because%20I%20mentioned%20Covid%2C%20I%20am%20linking%20Chum%20to%20being%20Chinese.%20People%20are%20so%20foolish.%20I%20meant%20Karan%20Veer%20might%20have%20Covid%20and%20he%20lost%20his%20sense%20of%20taste%20and%20smell%20and%20that's%20why%20he%20likes%20Chum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKenjum%20Pakam%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Arunachal%20women's%20panel%2C%20wrote%20to%20NCW%20chief%20Vijaya%20Kishore%20Rahatkar%2C%20flagging%20Yadav's%20comments%20against%20Chum%20Darang%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Miss%20Arunachal%20beauty%20pageant%20and%20is%20also%20a%20former%20Big%20Boss%20contestant.%20%26quot%3BHis%20comment%20not%20only%20insults%20Ms.%20Darang%20but%20the%20entire%20women%20society%20of%20Northeast%20India.%20His%20comment%20of%20social%20media%20tarnished%20the%20reputation%20of%20Chum%20Darang%20in%20particular%20and%20women%20of%20North%20East%20in%20general.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20behaviour%20and%20derogatory%20comments%20create%20a%20pervasive%20sense%20of%20fear%20and%20Intimidation%20amongst%20women%20of%20the%20North%20East%20who%20are%20pursuing%20their%20dreams%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20of%20Bollywood%20making%20them%20vulnerable%20and%20marginalized%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20urging%20the%20national%20women's%20panel%20to%20take%20action%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElvish%20Yadav%20is%20not%20new%20to%20controversies.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20sparked%20a%20row%20with%20remarks%20against%20actors%20Kusha%