Gaza%26quot%3B%20would%20not%20include%20a%20right%20of%20return%20for%20displaced%20Palestinians%2C%20now%20said%20the%20redeveloped%20land%20will%20be%20for%20people%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20get%20it%20going%20eventually%2C%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20jobs%20are%20going%20to%20be%20created%20for%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20for%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Palestinians%20living%20in%20Gaza%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20leave%20because%20they%20are%20currently%20%26quot%3Bliving%20a%20terrible%20life%26quot%3B%20after%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20war%20following%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20way%20they're%20living%20now.%20Nobody's%20nobody's%20living%20like%20that%20in%20the%20entire%20world.%20They're%20living%20under%20buildings%20that%20are%20mostly%20fallen%20down%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20fall%20down%2C%20and%20they're%20living%20under%20people%20are%20being%20killed%20every%20day.%20The%20conditions%20are%20horrible.%20There%20are%20no%20conditions%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20that%20are%20worse%20than%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20leader%20stunned%20the%20world%20when%20he%20announced%20a%20proposal%20last%20week%20for%20the%20United%20States%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20over%26quot%3B%20Gaza%2C%20envisioning%20rebuilding%20the%20devastated%20territory%20into%20the%20%26quot%3BRiviera%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%26quot%3B%20--%20but%20only%20after%20resettling%20Palestinians%20elsewhere%2C%20with%20no%20plan%20for%20them%20ever%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPushback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20President's%20plan%20to%20%26quot%3Bown%26quot%3B%20Gaza%20and%20place%20it%20under%20%26quot%3BUS%20authority%26quot%3B%20faced%20pushback%20from%20the%20visiting%20Abdullah%20II%2C%20who%20informed%20that%20Egypt%20was%20working%20on%20a%20plan%20for%20how%20countries%20in%20the%20region%20could%20%26quot%3Bwork%26quot%3B%20with%20Trump%20on%20his%20shock%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reiterated%20Jordan's%20steadfast%20position%20against%20the%20displacement%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%20This%20is%20the%20unified%20Arab%20position.%20Rebuilding%20Gaza%20without%20displacing%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20addressing%20the%20dire%20humanitarian%20situation%20should%20be%20the%20priority%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Abdullah%20said%20on%20social%20media%20after%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20suggested%20that%20neighbouring%20countries%20such%20as%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%20could%20absorb%20Gaza's%20population.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20can%20work%20with%20the%20President%20and%20with%20the%20United%20States.%20So%20I%20think%20let's%20wait%20until%20the%20Egyptians%20can%20come%20and%20present%20it%20to%20the%20President%20and%20not%20get%20ahead%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jordanian%20monarch%20also%20appeared%20to%20offer%20a%20sweetener%20to%20Trump%2C%20who%20the%20day%20before%20the%20visit%20floated%20the%20possibility%20of%20halting%20US%20aid%20to%20Jordan%20if%20it%20did%20not%20take%20in%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20can%20do%20right%20away%20is%20take%202%2C000%20children%2C%20cancer%20children%20who%20are%20in%20a%20very%20ill%20state.%20That%20is%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Abdullah%20said%20as%20Trump%20welcomed%20him%20and%20Crown%20Prince%20Hussein%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20replied%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20a%20beautiful%20gesture%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20didn't%20know%20about%20it%20before%20the%20Jordanian%20monarch's%20arrival%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20President%20also%20retreated%20from%20his%20previous%20talk%20of%20an%20aid%20halt%20to%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20to%20threaten%20that.%20I%20do%20believe%20we're%20above%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Egyptian%20foreign%20ministry%20later%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Bpresent%20a%20comprehensive%20vision%20for%20the%20reconstruction%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20that%20ensures%20Palestinians%20remain%20on%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20Egypt%20%26quot%3Bhopes%20to%20cooperate%26quot%3B%20with%20Trump's%20administration%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20%26quot%3Breaching%20a%20fair%20settlement%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20Of%20Gaza%20Truce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Israel%20has%20threatened%20to%20resume%20%26quot%3Bintense%20fighting%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%20if%20hostages%20were%20not%20released%20this%20weekend%2C%20while%20Hamas%20insisted%20it%20remained%20committed%20to%20the%20ceasefire%20deal%20and%20accused%20Israel%20of%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20truce%2C%20which%20has%20largely%20halted%20more%20than%2015%20months%20of%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20captives%20were%20to%20be%20released%20in%20batches%20in%20exchange%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20Israeli%20custody.%20So%20far%2C%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20have%20completed%20five%20hostage-prisoner%20swaps.%20But%20the%20deal%20has%20come%20under%20increasing%20strain%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20prompting%20diplomatic%20efforts%20to%20salvage%20it%20and%20Hamas%20to%20say%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20the%20ceasefire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20Hamas%20does%20not%20return%20our%20hostages%20by%20Saturday%20noon%2C%20t