hat%20before%20managing%20Belle%2C%20Chanelle%20also%20managed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilla-blake-real-person-apple-cider-vinegar-jess-ainscough-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMilla%20Blake%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Alycia%20Debnam-Carey)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20childhood%20friend%20who%20also%20built%20her%20brand%20around%20attempting%20to%20treat%20her%20cancer%20via%20alternative%20methods.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Milla%2C%20the%20Chanelle%20character%20isn't%20exactly%20the%20same%20in%20real%20life.%20But%20she%20shares%20a%20lot%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20first%20name%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20woman%20who%20is%20likely%20her%20real-life%20counterpart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224265%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alycia%20debnam-carey%20and%20aisha%20dee%20as%20milla%20and%20chanelle%20in%20apple%20cider%20vinegar.%20they're%20two%20young%20women%20standing%20on%20a%20porch%2C%20smiling%20and%20looking%20at%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aa81417bb3f854015c6e1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlycia%20Debnam-Carey%20and%20Dee%20as%20Milla%20and%20Chanelle%20in%20%26quot%3BApple%20Cider%20Vinegar.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e38341b5-7535-4d7c-9b28-4ac4aff13642%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanelle%20works%20with%20both%20Milla%20and%20Belle%20in%20'Apple%20Cider%20Vinegar'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Netflix%20series%2C%20Chanelle%20joins%20Milla's%20team%20after%20her%20business%20starts%20to%20take%20off%20to%20help%20her%20to%20secure%20brand%20deals.%20She%20meets%20Belle%20at%20a%20Cosmopolitan%20awards%20ceremony%20she's%20attending%20with%20Milla%2C%20who's%20up%20for%20an%20award%20in%20the%20same%20category%20as%20Belle%20(Belle%20wins).%20The%20three%20women%20meet%20at%20the%20after-party%2C%20where%20Chanelle%20and%20Belle%20bond%20after%20Milla%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Milla%20works%20on%20launching%20her%20juice%20line%2C%20Chanelle%20works%20with%20Belle%20to%20support%20the%20launch%20of%20her%20app%2C%20The%20Whole%20Pantry%2C%20on%20the%20Apple%20Watch.%20But%20as%20Chanelle%20is%20exposed%20to%20the%20more%20glamorous%20aspects%20of%20Belle's%20lifestyle%2C%20she%20starts%20to%20have%20doubts%20about%20her%20story.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20she%20confronts%20Belle%20and%20explicitly%20asks%20if%20she%20has%20brain%20cancer.%20Belle%20deflects%2C%20but%20the%20two%20seemingly%20come%20to%20an%20agreement%20to%20cancel%20her%20deal%20with%20Apple%20and%20the%20publishing%20of%20her%20cookbook.%20Instead%2C%20however%2C%20Belle%20doubles%20down%20on%20the%20lie%20and%20claims%20on%20social%20media%20that%20she's%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20multiple%20additional%20cancers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20The%20Whole%20Pantry%20cookbook%20launch%2C%20Chanelle%20tells%20two%20reporters%20at%20The%20Age%20that%20Belle%20is%20a%20fraud.%20While%20they're%20unable%20to%20report%20any%20information%20about%20Belle's%20health%2C%20they%20publish%20a%20story%20with%20evidence%20that%20she%20hadn't%20followed%20through%20on%20multiple%20promised%20charitable%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChanelle%20stops%20working%20with%20Belle%2C%20but%20later%20runs%20into%20her%20at%20Milla's%20funeral.%20(Milla%2C%20unlike%20Belle%2C%20actually%20had%20cancer.)%20Later%2C%20Chanelle%20is%20seen%20planting%20trees%20with%20Milla's%20father%20and%20fianc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22aisha%20dee%20and%20alycia%20debnam-carey%20as%20chanelle%20and%20milla%20in%20aple%20cider%20vinegar.%20they're%20two%20young%20women%20conversing%20closely%20in%20a%20colorfully%20decorated%20kitchen.%20on%20the%20table%20in%20front%20them%20are%20rows%20of%20colorful%20juices%20in%20glass%20bottles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aa81a26630e