said%20she%20confronted%20Gibson%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20produce%20documentation%20that%20she%20had%20cancer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gibson%20dodged%20the%20question%20and%20refused%2C%20McAuliffe%20went%20to%20the%20press%2C%20giving%20reporter%20Beau%20Donnelly%20a%20tip%20about%20Gibson.%20He%20and%20his%20colleague%20Nick%20Toscana%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Ftechnology%2Fcharity-money-promised-by-inspirational-health-app-developer-belle-gibson-not-handed-over-20150306-13xgqk.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Sydney%20Morning%20Herald%20that%20Gibson%20had%20failed%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20multiple%20promised%20charitable%20donations.%20The%20pair%20went%20on%20to%20write%20the%202017%20book%20%26quot%3BThe%20Woman%20Who%20Fooled%20The%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20serves%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20%26quot%3BApple%20Cider%20Vinegar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BApple%20Cider%20Vinegar%2C%26quot%3B%20Chanelle%20also%20works%20as%20Milla's%20manager%2C%20and%20is%20one%20of%20her%20childhood%20friends.%20In%20reality%2C%20McAuliffe%20did%20not%20work%20with%20Jess%20Ainscough%2C%20the%20real%20Australian%20influencer%20whose%20story%20resembles%20Milla's.%20Ainscough's%20manager%20was%20Yvette%20Luciano%3B%20Ainscough%20died%20of%20epithelioid%20sarcoma%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20real%20life%2C%20Gibson%20had%20little%20more%20than%20a%20tenuous%20connection%20to%20Aincough%2C%20too%3A%20Donnelly%20and%20Toscana%20report%20in%20their%20book%20that%20Luciano%20was%20confused%20to%20see%20Gibson%20make%20an%20appearance%20at%20Ainscough's%20funeral.%20After%20Ainscough's%20death%2C%20Yvette%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20that%20Gibson%20and%20Ainscough%20were%20not%20friends%2C%20and%20did%20not%20have%20a%20relationship%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20an%20Instagram%20or%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BApple%20Cider%20Vinegar%26quot%3B%20is%20streaming%