s%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20and%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20some%20other%20affiliate%20stations%2C%20according%20to%20USIM%2C%20the%20media%20agency%20that%20brokered%20the%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Livingston%2C%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20USIM%2C%20said%20the%20agency%20immediately%20ceased%20working%20with%20Yeezy%20LLC%20after%20seeing%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisparaging%20and%20vile%20comments%26quot%3B%20Ye%20had%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELivingston%20said%20Fox%20had%20said%20the%20media%20buy%20was%20%26quot%3Bnon-cancelable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20informed%20Fox%20that%20they%20should%20cease%20airing%20any%20remnant%20spots%20immediately%20upon%20learning%20that%20Yeezy%2C%20LLC%20was%20promoting%20vile%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fox%20insider%20told%20BI%20they%20received%20no%20communication%20from%20the%20agency%20about%20requesting%20to%20drop%20the%20ad%20until%20Monday%20morning%20after%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20spot%20had%20aired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Yeezy%20Super%20Bowl%20spot%2C%20which%20purported%20to%20be%20shot%20on%20an%20iPhone%20and%20featured%20the%20rapper%20sitting%20in%20a%20dentist's%20chair%20showing%20off%20his%20new%20teeth%2C%20was%20unlikely%20to%20have%20caused%20alarm%20when%20it%20was%20submitted%20and%20subsequently%20approved%20for%20broadcast%20because%20it%20didn't%20contain%20any%20obscenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20whassup%20guys%2C%20I%20spent%20like%20all%20the%20money%20for%20the%20commercial%20on%20these%20new%20teeth.%20So%2C%20once%20again%20I%20had%20to%20shoot%20it%20on%20the%20iPhone.%20Um%2C%20um%2C%20um%2C%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FYeezy.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYeezy.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Ye%20said%20in%20the%20sparse%20ad.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FYeezy.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYeezy.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20ran%20a%20local%20spot%20during%20last%20year's%20Super%20Bowl%2C%20starring%20Ye.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20ad's%20approval%20and%20airing%2C%20the%20Yeezy%20store%20displayed%20a%20number%20of%20items%20for%20sale.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20ad%20was%20shown%20that%20the%20website%20was%20updated%20to%20display%20the%20swastika%20T-shirt%20for%20sale%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20of%20the%20site%20captured%20by%20the%20Internet%20Archive's%20Wayback%20Machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSIM's%20Livingston%20said%20the%20agency%20was%20unaware%20that%20Ye%20had%20intended%20to%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20store's%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20commercial%20was%20to%20promote%20general%20athletic%20apparel%20listed%20on%20the%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20Livingston%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20his%20website%2C%20Ye's%20X%20account%20appears%20to%20also%20be%20deactivated%20on%20the%20platform%20as%20of%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYe%20is%20an%20intergenerational%20artist%20and%20icon%20who%20continues%20to%20redefine%20the%20limits%20of%20creativity%20and%20free%20expression.%20He%20has%20deactivated%20his%20X%20account%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%26quot%3B%20spokesperson%20Milo%20Yiannopoulos%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNero%2Fstatus%2F1889255545128857863%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20NBC%20News.%20Representatives%20for%20Ye%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20further%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYe%20was%20previously%20banned%20from%20X%2C%20then%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20in%202022%20after%20he%20tweeted%20an%20image%20containing%20a%20swastika%20and%20the%20Star%20of%20David.%20His%20account%20was%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-reinstates-kanye-wests-twitter-x-account-after-ban-antisemitism-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereinstated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20following%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20airing%2C%20many%20called%20for%20the%20Yeezy%20site%20to%20be%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20the%20Anti-Defamation%20League%2C%20which%20called%20the%20T-shirt%20listing%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20proof%20of%20Kanye's%20antisemitism%2C%26quot%3B%20encouraged%20people%20to%20sign%20an%20open%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faction.adl.org%2Fa%2Fkanye-super-bowl%3Fsourceid%3D1082070%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20calling%20on%20Fox%20Sports%20to%20condemn%20Ye's%20ad.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20the%20letter%20had%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faction.adl.org%2Fa%2Fkanye-super-bowl%3Fsourceid%3D1082070%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%2C000%20%3C%2Fa%3Esignatories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20swastika%20is%20the%20symbol%20adopted%20by%20Hitler%20as%20the%20primary%20emblem%20of%20the%20Nazis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ADL%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FADL%2Fstatus%2F1889015130463101157%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20to%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BIt%20galvanized%20his%20followers%20in%20the%2020th%20century%20and%20continues%20to%20threaten%20and%20instill%20fear%20in%20those%20targeted%20by%20antisemitism%20and%20white%20supremacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20wasn't%20enough%2C%20the%20t-shirt%20is%20labeled%20on%20Kanye's%20website%20as%20'HH-01%2C'%20which%20is%20code%20for%20'Heil%20Hitler%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20talent%20agent%20Daniel%20McCartney%20of%2033%20%26amp%3B%20West%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdanielmccartney%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_button_share_sheet%26igsh%3DZDNlZDc0MzIxNw%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Instagram%20that%20he%20would%20no%20longer%20represent%20Ye%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20his%20recent%20harmful%20and