heeseburger%20came%20with%20a%20gooey%20layer%20of%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20burger%20as%20part%20of%20the%20chain's%20%26quot%3B2%20for%20%242X%26quot%3B%20deal%2C%20which%20also%20allowed%20me%20to%20get%20an%20order%20of%20boneless%20wings%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chicken-tenders-ranked-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echicken%20tender%3C%2Fa%3E%20basket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20burger%20typically%20costs%20%2416.99%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20at%20the%20location%20I%20visited%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Applebee's%20teamed%20up%20with%20the%20NFL%20as%20the%20league's%20official%20grill%20and%20bar%20partner%2C%20recognizing%20overlap%20between%20their%20customer%20base%20and%20NFL%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20our%20guests%20are%20football%20fans%2C%26quot%3B%20Applebee's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20Joel%20Yashinsky%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20season%2C%20we've%20been%20all%20in%20on%20the%20NFL.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20collected%20by%20Applebee's%20in%20April%20showed%20that%2064%25%20of%20its%20guests%20were%20interested%20in%20or%20very%20interested%20in%20the%20NFL%2C%20and%20around%2034%25%20had%20watched%20the%20NFL%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20which%20helped%20shape%20the%20chain's%20strategy%20for%20the%20football%20season%2C%20Yashinsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cheeseburger%20came%20with%20two%20slices%20of%20American%20cheese%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomato%2C%20red%20onion%2C%20and%20pickles%20on%20a%20brioche%20bun.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22applebees%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab901aeb4be2fff9a4449c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3